overview: Nicolette's bachelorette party just ended, and she and her maid of honor Chloe are winding down after a crazy night of club-hopping. It's busty Nicolette's last night as a single lady and Chloe wants to give her one final gift before she ties the knot. Good vibes are in the air, and Nicolette is happy to spend one more night getting even closer to her best friend. Katya Rodriguez is a flatterer. She rides for her girls. When Kiara is feeling down, Katya decides to hold an intimate indoor camping trip! Nothing like two girls, a tent, some ambient lighting, maybe a few photos to capture the moment. And there's only one way to reward such a sweet gesture. Right?
title: Juicy Licks 22
